      "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Dice your <strong>tomato[es] </strong>as finely as you can</p><p>Add the <strong>diced tomato</strong> to a small bowl with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong>, <strong>sugar</strong> and a crack of <strong>black pepper</strong> and give everything a good mix up, then set aside</p><p><strong><span class=\"text-danger\">Tip: Cooking for kids? Slice into rounds and leave plain!</span></strong></p>",
      "order": 1,
