      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>chopped onion</strong>,<strong> chopped garlic </strong>and<strong> grated courgette</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 5-6 min or until beginning to soften and caramelise</p>",
