    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once everything has slightly softened, reduce the heat to medium-high</p><p>Add your <strong>arborio rice</strong> and cook for 1 min, stirring to coat the grains in the oil</p><p>Add the<strong> vegetable</strong> <strong>stock</strong> a ladle at a time, stirring continuously for 25-30 min or until all of the stock is absorbed and the rice is cooked</p>",
